  "sections": [],
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 2
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When you return a result from your app intent, you can include a snippet to display on"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "the person’s device. A snippet is an interface element that displays static or interactive"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "content. Siri, Spotlight, and the Shortcuts app display snippets when it’s appropriate to"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "provide feedback visually. For interactive snippets, the buttons and controls in the snippet"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "run other app intents to make the necessary changes."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Your app’s interface contains important context about what a person is doing, but the system",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "needs your help to interpret that context. When you assign relevant app entities to the views"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "in your interface, Apple Intelligence and Siri use that information to improve the responses"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "they offer.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
